Bayer CropScience Grants Shemer Fungicide Rights to Koppert

-- B y   M a r i a j o s e   V e r a
-- 
2011-10-18T10:05:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/bayer-cropscience-grants-shemer-fungicide-rights-to-koppert.html
  Bayer CropScience  reached an
agreement with Koppert Biological Systems to grant exclusive
worldwide rights on the marketing, registration and production
of the new product Shemer, a biological fungicidal product based
on the yeast strain Metschnikowia fructicola, the company said
in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mariajose Vera at 
 mvera1@bloomberg.net  